description:
Special guests Wil McKenna and Tony Gallicchio of The Medicinals will stop the world and melt your face while you shake your sweet patootie like it was your sacred duty! Hollywood and Heins present what might be the 777th edition of the Roc City Pro Jam. 

Featuring Lou Spezio on keys, Adrien D'Angelo on bass and sound and a cast of dozens, the most fine Buta Pub will be rocking. 

Peace ~ Bless Up!
name: Tonight - Roc City Pro Jam with Wil & Tony of the Medicinals - FREE
